ygData.subject: Re: Finding Pelts
ygData.msgSnippet: Yep, ruined for patchwork but I m working on studded which takes Medium and soon reinforced which takes High Quality ... From: James Schuldes
ygData.messageBody:
Yep, ruined for patchwork but I'm working on studded which takes Medium and
soon reinforced which takes High Quality

right, I get high quality cat pelts all the time, but need
wolf pelts for
small armor and have never seen one

The higher level you are, the greater chance you have of
finding med. and
high
quality pelts. The same principle as getting more money off
mobs the higher

level you get.



--Mythra the bard, Tunare
